er) Paper Beast VR vine și pe PC (RPS) Re:Turn – One Way Trip (PC Gamer) Medic: Pacific Corpsman (PC Gamer) Voidtrain (PC Gamer) Foreclosed (PC Gamer) Lucifer Within Us (PC Gamer) Nongunz: Doppleganger Edition (Hardcore Gamer) Metal: Hellsinger (AllGamers) GONNER2 (RPS) Cardaclysm (PC Gamer) Almighty: Kill Your Gods (PC Gamer) Dustborn (Escapist) Lake (PC Gamer) Space Crew (Eurogamer) Serial Cleaners (Escapist) Gloomwood (Destructoid) No Place for Bravery (PC Gamer) Just Die Already (PC Gamer) Tribes of Midgard (GamesRadar+)  Anunțate la prezentarea PlayStation 5  Spider-Man Miles Morales(VideoGamesChronicle) Gran Turismo 7 (AllGamers, VideoGamesChronicle) Project Athia (AllGamers) Sackboy: A Big Adventure (AllGamers) Ratchet \u0026amp; Clank: Rift Apart (Shacknews) Returnal (AllGamers) Kena: Bridge of Spirits(Destructoid) Hitman 3 (AllGamers) Demon\u0026rsquo;s Souls Remake (VideoGamesChronicle) Resident Evil 8: Village (VideoGamesChronicle) Pragmata (VideoGamesChronicle) Jett: The Far Shore (Shacknews) Stray (PC Gamer) Horizon: Forbidden West (Polygon) Solar Ash (Destructoid) Astro\u0026rsquo;s Playroom (Shacknews) Goodbye Volcano High (Shacknews) Destruction AllStars (Shacknews) Bugsnax (Destructoid) Little Devil Inside (Shacknews, RPS) NBA 2K21 (Shacknews)  Anunțate la PC Gaming Show  Icarus (Shacknews) Carto (Destructoid) Blankos Block Party (Destructoid) Potionomics (Destructoid) Cartel Tycoon (Destructoid) In Sound Mind (Shacknews) Fae Tactics vine și pe PC (Shacknews) Surgeon Simulator 2 (Destructoid)  Acum cu dată de lansare  West of Dead: 18 iunie (PC Gamer) Neon Abyss: 14 iulie (GameSpace) Röki: 23 iulie (Eurogamer) XIII Remake: 10 noiembrie (PC Gamer) Cris Tales: 17 noiembrie (DSOGaming) Remothered: Broken Porcelain: 25 august (PC Gamer)  Lansate  9 iunie: 1971 Project Helios (Steam, gog.com) 11 iunie: Journey ajunge și pe Steam (Steam) 11 iunie: Skyhill: Black Mist (Steam) 11 iunie: Main Assembly (early access) (Steam) 11 iunie: Beyond Blue (Steam) 12 i