i în industria jocurilor, un director de la Riot Games fiind nevoit să își dea demisia din cauza unei postări pe Facebook, iar bundle-ul caritabil vândut de itch.io a strâns peste 6 milioane de dolari.","tags":"itch.io,PlayStation 5,PC Gaming Show,The Guerilla Collective,IGN Summer of Games,The Last of Us,The Longing,Graveyard Keeper,Command \u0026 Conquer Remastered,Rogue Legacy,Warframe,Need for Speed: World,Streets of Rage,Assassin’s Creed: Origins,Burn Me Twice","title":"Retrospectiva săptămânii 7 - 13 iunie 2020","url":"https://candaparerevista.ro/highlights/2020/06/14/"},{"author":"candaparerevista","category":"Revistele Lunii","content":"Linkuri rapide:\nLEVEL | Game Informer | PC Gamer | EDGE | RetroGamer | The Games Machine | Pelit | Pelaaja | Hobby Consolas | Power Unlimited | PC Games | Wireframe | CanardPC\nLEVEL (Turcia) Iunie 2020 (#280)  \u0026lt;figure\u0026gt; \u0026lt;a href = \u0026quot;https://www.level.com.tr/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/KAPAK.jpg\u0026quot;\u0026gt; \u0026lt;img src=\u0026quot;images/level-tr-280.jpg\u0026quot; alt=\u0026quot;\u0026quot; \u0026gt; \u0026lt;/a\u0026gt; \u0026lt;figcaption\u0026gt; \u0026lt;span\u0026gt; \u0026lt;/span\u0026gt; \u0026lt;/figcaption\u0026gt; \u0026lt;/figure\u0026gt;  \nGame Informer (SUA) #326  \u0026lt;figure\u0026gt; \u0026lt;a href = \u0026quot;https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod-media.gameinformer.com/2020/05/20/97a77926/326-cover-800h.jpg\u0026quot;\u0026gt; \u0026lt;img src=\u0026quot;images/game-informer-326.jpg\u0026quot; alt=\u0026quot;\u0026quot; \u0026gt; \u0026lt;/a\u0026gt; \u0026lt;figcaption\u0026gt; \u0026lt;span\u0026gt; \u0026lt;/span\u0026gt; \u0026lt;/figcaption\u0026gt; \u0026lt;/figure\u0026gt;  \nPC Gamer (UK) Iulie 2020 (#345)  \u0026lt;figure\u0026gt; \u0026lt;a href = \u0026quot;https://content.myfavouritemagazines.co.uk/out/pictures//master/product/1/pcg_p1%2849%29.jpg\u0026quot;\u0026gt; \u0026lt;img src=\u0026quot;images/pc-gamer-345.jpg\u0026quot; alt=\u0026quot;\u0026quot; 