er: Nightmare of the Wolf. (Gizmodo, PC Gamer, Destructoid, Escapist, Eurogamer, GamesIndustry.biz) Începând de săptămâna asta, YouTube deține drepturile exclusive de streaming pentru evenimentele de e-sports ale Activision Blizzard. (Variety, Kotaku, Polygon, GamesIndustry.biz) Și o serie de știri cu procese:  Nintendo câștigă câteva procese importante: mai întâi un litigiu vechi din 2013 în baza unui patent care ar fi fost încălcat de tehnologia din Wii Remote (VideoGamesChronicle, Ars Technica, GameDaily.biz, Shacknews), precum și un proces intentat în Europa privind dreptul cumpărătorilor de a cere anularea unei precomenzi în Nintento eShop și a-și primi banii înapoi. (VideoGamesChronicle, Eurogamer, GamesIndustry.biz) Deși procesul prin care Riot Games fuseseră dați în judecată pe motivul discriminării de gen la locul de muncă părea să fie la sfârșit, după ce compania ajunsese la o înțelegere pentru a plăti 10 milioane de dolari femeilor discriminate, două agenții guvernamentale din California au intervenit în proces solicitând creșterea despăgubirilor de peste 40 de ori. (PC Gamer, GameDaily.biz, GamesIndustry.biz, TechRaptor) În urma unui proces intentat de un jucător nemulțumit de Runescape, o instanță din SUA a decis că a fi muted într-un joc nu reprezintă o încălcare a drepturilor civile. (Eurogamer, PC Gamer)   Articole (critică, dev, design)  Giving video games a distinct Italian flavour doesn\u0026rsquo;t mean what you might think (Eurogamer) The Rise of the Information Game (EGM) Toss a Coin: The Enigmatic Appeal of Gaming’s Greatest Bards (EGM) Moral-Making Through Gameplay (First Person Scholar)  Actualitate  Will the success of The Witcher herald a golden age of game-to-TV adaptations? (The Guardian) The Witcher heralds an era of game IPs on TV (GamesIndustry.biz) PAX South 2020\u0026#039;s Indie Highlights Include Airport Dogs, Talking Grapes, and Neo Geo Puzzle Nostalgia (USgamer)  Not-a-review  To play Monument Valley is to marvel at how it works (Eurogamer) Silent Hill 2 Has the Best Depiction of an Abuse Survivor in Games (Escapist) Being petty jerks in Six Ages actually makes you the most powerful clan ever (RPS) Close to the Lip (Medium/Videodame)  Industrie  Report: Game developers still prefer PC above all else, and over half support unionization (GameDaily.biz) 8 people shaping PC gaming at the start of the decade (PC Gamer) Playing the role - a week for video game actors (VG247). Câteva recomandări:  An ode to the unsung heroes of video game cinematics and gameplay - stunt performers \u0026quot;My throat was bleeding\u0026quot; - the dangers of vocal strain in video game VO Video games should credit mocap actors alongside the voice talent   Istorie, retrospectivă  The transcendent appeal of Mount \u0026amp; Blade: Warband (GamesIndustry.biz) Zak McKracken And The Alien Mindbenders: The LucasArts game you don\u0026#8217;t want to play any more (RPS) How World of Warcraft was born from chaos (Polygon) How a Compromised RPG Prepared Larian Studios to Take On \u0026#39;Baldur\u0026#39;s Gate 3\u0026#39; (Vice) Fantasy and hard-boiled detective fiction collide in cult adventure game Discworld Noir (PC Gamer) The Game Archaeologist: Super-early versions of MMORPG websites (Massively OP) Master of Orion (The Digital Antiquarian)  Dev, making of, mecanici  Balancing Act: How Developers Make Games \u0026quot;Fair\u0026quot; (EGM) The \u0026quot;magic and chaos\u0026quot; of SuperMash, a game with seven different genres (GamesIndustry.biz) The usage of \u0026quot;suspense\u0026quot; in video games (Gamasutra)  Design, world-building, artă  The miles we walk: How physical maps can guide the development of sprawling game worlds (GamesRadar+) In Mythgard, Monsters Still Roam The Earth (Kotaku)  Anunțuri şi lansări de jocuri Anunţate  Captain Tsubasa: Rise of New Champions (Kotaku) HyperSpace: Pirates of Atira (Kotaku) Project Mara (Games Informer)  Acum cu dată de lansare  Wasteland Remastered: 15 februarie (RPS