amesIndustry.biz):\n Jeremy Soule, compozitorul seriei Elder Scrolls (Eurogamer, Kotaku, GamesIndustry.biz) Michael Antonov, unul dintre fondatorii companiei Oculus (The Verge, Kotaku, GamesIndustry.biz) Alexis Kennedy, creatorul lui Cultist Simulator (Eurogamer, GamesIndustry.biz, PCGamesInsider.biz) Alec Holowka, designer și compozitor pentru Night in the Woods (Eurogamer). În acest caz, urmările au fost imediate și tragice:  mai întâi studioul care a creat jocul, Infinite Fall, a anunțat că întrerupe legăturile cu compozitorul, inclusiv anularea unui mic proiect aflat în lucru (Shacknews, The Verge, Polygon, RPS, Ars Technica, GamesIndustry.biz) iar sâmbătă sora lui Holowka a anunțat că acesta a decedat, fără să menționeze cauza, dar aparent fiind vorba de sinucidere (Shacknews, IGN, GamesIndustry.biz)   Alte știri  O echipă de Dota 2 devine prima din istorie care câștigă de două ori la rând concursul The International și, totodată, cel mai mare premiu din istoria esporturilor: 15 milioane de dolari. (Eurogamer, PC Gamer, GameDaily.biz, GamesIndustry.biz) Telltale Games este readusă la viață de compania care a cumpărat numele și bunurile care au rămas în urma închiderii Telltale de la sfârșitul anului trecut. Telltale încă deține drepturile asupra unor francize precum The Wolf Among Us și Batman. (GameDaily.biz, Kotaku, Ars Technica, Destructoid, PC Gamer, The Verge, VideoGamesChronicle, Eurogamer, GamesIndustry.biz) Acțiunile Activision Blizzard cresc la maximul ultimelor 9 luni după lansarea lui World of Warcraft Classic. (VideoGamesChronicle)  Articole (critică, dev, design)  Dungeons \u0026amp; Deceptions: The First D\u0026amp;D Players Push Back On The Legend Of Gary Gygax (Kotaku) On Your Marx: The Developers Bringing Socialism to Games (EGM) What the Heck are Surprise Mechanics? (The Psychology of Video Games) Depiction of War in Games: Can You Do Better? (Gamasutra) Video Games \u0026amp; Nostalgia: An Intertwined Relationship (Gamasutra) Poetry in motion - FMV\u0026#39;s unlikely revival (Wireframe magazine) Filosofia politică a jocurilor - Barbari la porțile Cetății (Mindcraft Stories)  Actualitate  Anonymity and Mob Mentality: The Dual Nature of Apex Legends’ Asshat Gaffe (TechRaptor) Telltale Games employees speak out about the studio’s controversial revival (Polygon) NBA 2K20 trailer sells the thrill of gambling (GamesIndustry.biz) Developers sound off after abuse accusations (GamesIndustry.biz)  Not-a-review  (Spoilers!) The Haunting Discoveries Of Outer Wilds (Kotaku) Romero returns to Doom to play tricks in Sigil (PC Gamer) \u0026#39;Knights and Bikes\u0026#39; Is a Sweetly Scary Game About Childhood\u0026#39;s End (Vice) Surreal adventure Vane is darkly beautiful and occasionally frustrating (PC Gamer) \u0026#39;Ancestors\u0026#39; Is an Audacious Experiment. I Never Want to Play It Again. (Vice) Open Worlds (Real Life Magazine) Undefeated (Deep Hell) Eliza Shows Why Human Bias Is Necessary (Unwinnable) Snakeskin and Monkey Business: The Animals of Sekiro (Kotaku)  Control  “A Loose Grip on Reality” (Bullet Points Monthly) Control Proves That An Office Building Is The Perfect Setting For A Metroid-Like (Kotaku) The Fonts In Control Make Its World Feel Way Creepier (Kotaku) Control’s Hidden Puppet Show Is A Horror Masterpiece (Kotaku)  World of Warcraft  The casualties of WoW Classic\u0026rsquo;s battle for authenticity (Destructoid) World of Warcraft Classic is a beast of a game and a reminder of how far MMOs have come (Destructoid) World Of Warcraft Classic is more than just a phase (RPS) How the internet has reacted to World of Warcraft Classic (PC Gamer) Can ‘World of Warcraft Classic’ Revive the Past? (The Ringer) WoW Classic Brings The Community Back To World Of Warcraft (Kotaku) Opinion: Can World of Warcraft Classic capture the MMO\u0026rsquo;s original glory? (Gamasutra)  Industrie  Her Story, Telling Lies creator Sam Barlow talks Hitchcock, Metroid, and his lengthy casting process (Destructoid) \u0