ts,Atma","title":"Retrospectiva săptămânii 15 - 20 iulie","url":"https://candaparerevista.ro/highlights/2019/07/21/"},{"author":"candaparerevista","category":"Highlights","content":"Cuphead devine un serial animat adevărat, Nintendo lansează o versiune și mai portabilă a Switch-ului și, într-o lovitură de teatru total așteptată, jocul Ion Maiden își schimbă numele, scandalul G2A are încă ecouri iar Gibbous - A Cthulhu Adventure are dată de lansare.\nLinkuri rapide:\n Știri Articole (critică, dev, design) Made în România Anunţuri şi lansări de jocuri Prăvălii de jocuri  Știri  În ceea ce este probabil cea mai previzibilă tranziție cu putință, Cuphead devine un serial animat produs de Netflix. (Ars Technica, Eurogamer) Nintendo anunță o nouă variantă de Switch, ce va putea fi folosit doar ca dispozitiv portabil - Switch Lite (Eurogamer, Ars Technica, Polygon, VideoGamesChronicle, IGN). Iar, dacă zvonurile sunt adevărate, ne pregătește și un upgrade pentru Switch-ul normal. (Ars Technica, VideoGamesChronicle) 3D Realms decide să încheie procesul cu formația Iron Maiden și să-și redenumească jocul din Ion Maiden în Ion Fury. (Destructoid, PC Gamer, Shacknews, Eurogamer)  Articole (critică, dev, design)  Auto Chess proves again that it\u0026rsquo;s modders who know what we really want (Eurogamer) Game developers, it’s time to stop listening to the fans (VG247) \u0026#39;Mordhau\u0026#39; and the Fantasy of an All-White Middle Ages (Vice) WTF is a Classic Game? (Gamasutra) An unbeatable poker bot offers glimpses of video game AI’s future (Polygon) Facebook AI Pluribus defeats top poker professionals in 6-player Texas Hold ’em (Ars Technica) It\u0026#039;s Becoming Impossible To Keep Up With More Than A Couple \u0026quot;Forever\u0026quot; Games (USgamer) How \u0026#8216;climate crisis games\u0026#8217; could better model our problems and our future (RPS)  Actualitate  Nintendo Switch Lite is destined for success, but Switch Pro is the important one (GamesIndustry.biz)  Not-a-review  Real Justice (Bullet Points Monthly) Putting the \u0026quot;U\u0026quot; In Trauma (Unwinnable) We Must Be Better (First Person Scholar) From Student Project to Backpacking in Space: The Story Behind the Mystery Sci-Fi Outer Wilds (USgamer)  Industrie  The industry is still \u0026quot;developing games in a bubble\u0026quot; (GamesIndustry.biz) Nintendo reaffirms its toy-maker identity (GamesIndustry.biz) Hello Games: Positive No Man\u0026rsquo;s Sky stories \u0026quot;don\u0026rsquo;t do as well \u0026ndash; and that\u0026rsquo;s a problem\u0026quot; (GamesIndustry.biz) \u0026quot;Xbox Game Pass is the first time subscription is fair for developers\u0026quot; (GamesIndustry.biz)  Istorie, retrospectivă  Worldwide Infamy: The Birth Of Carmen Sandiego (Games Informer) 15 years later, Warframe is finally close to realizing its original vision (PC Gamer) Final Fantasy IX Retrospective: The Final Fantasy\u0026#39;s Final Fantasy (Kotaku) Peter Jackson’s King Kong was the most innovative game of its console generation (Polygon) How a Zelda Clone Outshone Actual Zelda: The Case for a Forgotten PS One Gem (Medium) The Game Archaeologist: Ironman modes and elective permadeath (Massively OP) Per Aspera Ad Astra (ROMchip) The History of Games Could Be a History of What Play Felt Like (ROMchip) History Lesson: 9 great game ideas that never took off (VideoGamesChronicle) How N64\u0026rsquo;s Turok: Dinosaur Hunter was years ahead of its time (Eurogamer)  Dev, making of, mecanici  How developers build the tutorials you skip (PC Gamer) The secret to Warframe\u0026rsquo;s ship-to-ship space combat is that the ship doesn\u0026rsquo;t actually move (PC Gamer) More Than Meets the Eye: The Secrets of Dynamic Difficulty Adjustment (Rempton Games) Behind the Curtain: Uncovering Secret Hidden Game Mechanics (Rempton Games) Video: Inside the design of Subnautica (Gamasutra) The Psychology Of Fortnite\u0026#8217;s Battle Pass (The Psychology of Video Games) My Friend Pedro \u0026rsquo;s journey from Flash cult hit to indie success (Gamasutra)  Design, world-building, artă  Exploring the afterlife of historical sites in video games (Eurogamer) Game Box Art Critique July: Marvel Ultimate Alliance 3: The Black Order, Fire Emblem: Three Houses, Wolfenstein: Youngblood (VideoGamer)  Made în România  Gibbous - A Cthulhu Adventure are acum dată de lansare (7 august) și primește atenție și într-o știre de la PC Gamer. (Go4Games)  Anunțuri și lansări de jocuri  A free-to-play Lord of the Rings MMO is being developed by Amazon (PC Gamer)  Anunţate  Turok: Escape from Lost Valley (PC Gamer) Disintegration, un shooter SF de la unul dintre creatorii lui Halo (Eurogamer) Vane vine și pe PC (Destructoid)  Acum cu dată de lansare  Gloomhaven (early access): 17 iulie (Eurogamer) Biotope: 23 iulie (DSOGaming ) Morphies Law: Remorphed: 30 iulie (RPS) Stranded Sails: 4 octombrie (Eurogamer) Greedfall: 10 octombrie (PC Gamer)  Amânate  Psychonauts 2 apare în 2020 în loc de 2019 (DSOGaming )  Lansate  10 iulie: SolSeraph (Steam) 10 iulie: Godhood (early access) (Steam) 10 iulie: Goat of Duty (Steam) 11 iulie: Blazing Chrome (Steam) 11 iulie: Earth Defense Force 5 (Steam) 11 iulie: Eagle Island (Steam) 11 iulie: Field of Glory: Empires (Steam) 11 iulie: Tiny Metal: Full Metal Rumble (Steam) 11 iulie: Griftlands (early access) (Epic Store)  Prăvălii de jocuri Știri  Shady Market G2A Offers To Pay Journalists To Run Pre-Written Article Defending Them (Kotaku) Steam\u0026rsquo;s new \u0026lsquo;Interactive Recommender\u0026rsquo; uses machine learning, not tags or reviews, to tell you what to play (PC Gamer) Steam\u0026#39;s New Customizable AI Tool Scans Your Playtime And Tells You What To Buy Next (Kotaku)  Articole  This Year\u0026#39;s Steam Summer Sale Was A Mess, Game Developers Say (Kotaku) How does the games industry get rid of G2A? Eliminate game keys altogether (PC Gamer) G2A\u0026rsquo;s recent comments and business practices put itself at odds with deve