 vechiul Minecraft e acum gratis, Euro Truck Simulator 2 se extinde în România, Titan Quest lansează un nou expansion surpriză, iar Unbound: Worlds Apart dă drumul la Kickstarter.","tags":"Riot Games,Fig,loot boxes,Echo,Ultra Ultra,Starbreeze,NetherRealm,Quantic Dream,Gearbox,Randy Pitchford,Electronic Arts,Bethesda,Elsweyr,SEGA,Two Point Studios,QuakeCon,Analogue,Magic: The Gathering,Valve Index,LudoNarraCon,ESA,Forager,Elite: Dangerous,Mordhau,Bastion,Katana Zero,Into the Breach,Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice,Blizzard,Platinum Games,Terrawurm,Sierra,Jagged Alliance,Fortnite,Nintendo 3DS,Plants vs. Zombies,SkiFree,Humongous Entertainment,Forza Motorsport,Outward,Lemmings,God of War,Raising Kratos,Baba is You,Close to the Sun,Prey,Minecraft,Bearded Giant,Spece Mercs,Alien Pixel Studios,Unbound: Worlds Apart,File://maniac","title":"Retrospectiva săptămânii 5 - 11 mai 2019","url":"https://candaparerevista.ro/highlights/2019/05/12/"},{"author":"candaparerevista","category":"Revistele Lunii","content":"Linkuri rapide:\nLEVEL | Game Informer | PC Gamer | EDGE | RetroGamer | PC Guru | The Games Machine | Pelit | Pelaaja | Hobby Consolas | Power Unlimited | PC Games | Wireframe | Canard PC\nLEVEL LEVEL (Turcia), mai 2019 (#268)  \u0026lt;figure\u0026gt; \u0026lt;a href = \u0026quot;https://www.level.com.tr/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/KAPAK.jpg\u0026quot;\u0026gt; \u0026lt;img src=\u0026quot;images/level-tr-2019-05.jpg\u0026quot; alt=\u0026quot;\u0026quot; \u0026gt; \u0026lt;/a\u0026gt; \u0026lt;figcaption\u0026gt; \u0026lt;span\u0026gt; \u0026lt;/span\u0026gt; \u0026lt;/figcaption\u0026gt; \u0026lt;/figure\u0026gt;  \nGame Informer (SUA) Iunie 2019  \u0026lt;figure\u0026gt; \u0026lt;a href = \u0026quot;https://s3.amazonaws.com/prod-media.gameinformer.com/2019/05/07/e1f7637e/314.jpg\u0026quot;\u0026gt; \u0026lt;img src=\u0026quot;images/gameinformer-2019-06.jpg\u0026quot; alt=\u0026quot;\u0026quot; \u0026gt; \u0026lt;/a\u0026gt; \u0026lt;figcaption\u0026gt; \u0026lt;span\u0026gt;